title: Blind Rampage
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

If a [[Hive Tyrant]] (or the [[Swarmlord]]) is killed whilst part of a unit of [[Tyrant Guard]] (see the [[Shieldwall]] special rule), from the end of that turn the surviving [[Tyrant Guard]] have the [[Furious Charge]] and [[Rage]] special rules for the remainder of the battle.